title: One Two Seven Darby
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. This cafe in Cooks Hill offers some vegan menu items plus daily vegan muffins. Makes its own cashew cheese and coconut yoghurt, and use organic and local produce where possible. Vegan dishes include the avocado on sourdough (with cashew cheese), spiced eggplant, nourishing bowls, granola with coconut yoghurt.
